title: 'Quiet on Set' explores allegations of abuse, toxic behavior at Nickelodeon
description: A new documentary series reveals the disturbing shadows behind the bright cheeriness of children's television.

title: Caitlin Clark, Connecticut, cowboy hats: Here's what to watch for on Selection Sunday
description: Can the Iowa sensation finally win a ring? Will UConn repeat? Who could be this year's Cinderella? With March Madness around the corner, here's a preview of what to watch for on Selection Sunday.

title: A Florida man who refused to sell his home to a developer now lives in the shadows
description: Orlando Capote has been engaged in a two-decade struggle against developers and the city of Coral Gables to save his family's home. But his success comes with a price.

title: Haiti's prime minister steps down, leaving a power vacuum amid mounting violence
description: The Haitian prime minister has agreed to step down in an attempt to quell violence there. But several obstacles remain to ensure a peaceful transition of power to new leadership.

title: The eclipse gives astronomy clubs an opportunity to shine
description: From Texas to Maine, they're teaching people how to enjoy the spectacle safely. Some will hand out glasses or answer questions at events. Others plan to take their own advice — and get outta town.

title: Haitians have learned to persevere through the worst crises, often with humor
description: Haiti is coming back to life after violent gangs took over most of the capital and the prime minister became stranded abroad. Some are even laughing it off.

title: Who is Mohammad Mustafa, the new prime minister of the Palestinian Authority?
description: Mustafa was appointed by Palestinian President Mahmoud Abbas in a move seen as an attempt to appease U.S. demands for reform.

title: How IVF is complicating Republicans' abortion messaging
description: For years, Republicans pushed "life at conception." IVF is complicating that message as GOP lawmakers struggle to agree on a path forward.

title: This medieval astrolabe has both Arabic and Hebrew markings. Here's what it means
description: This discovery sheds new light on the rich history of scholarship and intellectual exchange between Muslims, Jews and Christians during a time of Muslim rule in medieval Spain.

title: Bolsonaro presented plan to reverse 2022 election, Brazilian military leaders say
description: Testimonies of two former military commanders to police include the first direct mentions of Jair Bolsonaro as actively participating in a conspiracy to ignore the results of the 2022 election.

title: Hong Kong jails 12 people for storming the legislature during 2019 protests
description: Hundreds of protesters swarmed into the legislature the night of July 1, 2019 at the height of the anti-government protests.

title: RBG's family condemns the selection of recipients of an award named in her honor
description: The Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg Leadership Award was created to honor women who have created positive change in society. RBG's family says this year's change in selection criteria betrays her legacy.
